---
const siteTitle = "AmicBridge – Private Borrow & Lend Network";
const siteDescription =
  "AmicBridge is a private person–to–person network where verified members can request to borrow, lend, or collaborate on investments. AmicBridge never holds client funds.";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>{siteTitle}</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content={siteDescription} />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0b1020;
        --bg-alt: #111729;
        --card: #171f33;
        --accent: #2f81f7;
        --accent-soft: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.1);
        --border: #263044;
        --text: #f5f7ff;
        --muted: #a9b3c7;
        --danger: #ff4d4f;
        --font: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          sans-serif;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html,
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #11192f 0, #050814 55%);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: var(--font);
      }

      body {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      main {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 960px;
        padding: 32px 16px 64px;
      }

      header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .logo {
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .logo-mark {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 11px;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
        margin: 0 0 8px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.18),
          rgba(9, 12, 24, 0.9)
        );
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 24px 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2.1fr) minmax(0, 1.4fr);
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .hero-subtitle {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .hero-highlight {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 4px 9px;
        background: rgba(1, 8, 27, 0.9);
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.3);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .hero-highlight span {
        width: 4px;
        height: 4px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent);
      }

      .hero-mono {
        font-family: "SF Mono", ui-monospace, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas,
          "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.9);
        border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.6);
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .hero-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 4px 0 0;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .hero-list li::before {
        content: "•";
        margin-right: 6px;
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--bg-alt);
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 14px 16px;
      }

      .card h2 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin: 0 0 8px;
      }

      .card h3 {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin: 0 0 6px;
      }

      .muted {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      ul {
        padding-left: 18px;
        margin: 6px 0 0;
      }

      li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .pill-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-top: 6px;
      }

      .pill {
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.9);
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 0 0 10px;
      }

      .form-wrapper {
        background: var(--bg-alt);
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 18px 16px 20px;
        margin-bottom: 26px;
      }

      form {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 12px 14px;
      }

      .field {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4px;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
      }

      label {
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      label span {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      input,
      select,
      textarea {
        background: #050814;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #252f41;
        padding: 7px 8px;
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        font-family: var(--font);
      }

      textarea {
        min-height: 80px;
        resize: vertical;
      }

      input:focus,
      select:focus,
      textarea:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.4);
      }

      .field-inline {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .field-inline > div {
        flex: 1;
      }

      .full-width {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
      }

      .hint {
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .checkbox-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 7px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }

      .checkbox-row input[type="checkbox"] {
        margin-top: 3px;
        width: 14px;
        height: 14px;
      }

      button {
        margin-top: 6px;
        padding: 9px 16px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        justify-self: flex-start;
      }

      button:hover {
        filter: brightness(1.05);
      }

      button:active {
        transform: translateY(1px);
      }

      footer {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-top: 16px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      footer p {
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .warning {
        color: var(--danger);
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      @media (max-width: 720px) {
        header {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 4px;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 18px 14px;
        }

        .hero-grid {
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
        }

        main {
          padding: 24px 14px 40px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <header>
        <div>
          <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-mark">AB</div>
            <span>AmicBridge</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tagline">Private money network</div>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Private, person–to–person finance</p>
            <h1>Request to borrow, lend, or invest inside a verified network.</h1>
            <p class="muted">
              AmicBridge is a private matching network. Members can request to
              borrow money, lend money, or work together on investments. We
              match verified people – we do not hold any funds.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-highlight">
              <span></span>
              <strong>Request access:</strong> join the AmicBridge private
              network
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="hero-mono">
              amicbridge.com is a network bridge.<br />
              • No custody of assets.<br />
              • No pooled accounts.<br />
              • You control where your money moves.
            </div>
            <ul class="hero-list">
              <li>We verify members with ID and basic income information.</li>
              <li>
                You decide your own terms with the other party and may use a
                loan agreement contract.
              </li>
              <li>AmicBridge charges 5% on each successful deal in the network.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>For borrowers</h2>
          <p class="muted">
            Submit a borrowing request and describe what kind of lender and
            agreement you are looking for.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Choose currency: NOK, USD, EUR, or supported crypto.</li>
            <li>Provide your age, work situation, and income level.</li>
            <li>Explain loan purpose, amount, and duration you prefer.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h2>For lenders</h2>
          <p class="muted">
            Describe what kind of borrowers you want to support and on what
            terms.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Define preferred loan sizes, currencies, and repayment horizons.
            </li>
            <li>
              Choose borrower profile: income range, risk level, and purpose of
              loan.
            </li>
            <li>
              You always control if you accept or reject a suggested match.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h2>Investments & strategy</h2>
          <p class="muted">
            You can also send a request for investment cooperation and strategy
            support.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Ask for help with building an investment plan or strategy
              description.
            </li>
            <li>
              Connect with other verified members interested in co-investments.
            </li>
            <li>
              AmicBridge takes 5&nbsp;% of every deal made through the network.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="form-wrapper">
        <h2 class="section-title">Request to join AmicBridge</h2>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          Use this form to apply for access to the private AmicBridge network
          and describe what you want to do: borrow, lend, or invest. We will
          review your details and contact you for ID verification and any
          follow-up questions.
        </p>

        <form
          action="https://formspree.io/f/xzznjkvd"
          method="POST"
        >
          <!-- Basic details -->
          <div class="field">
            <label for="fullName">Full name <span>*</span></label>
            <input
              id="fullName"
              name="full_name"
              type="text"
              required
              autocomplete="name"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="age">Age <span>*</span></label>
            <input
              id="age"
              name="age"
              type="number"
              min="18"
              required
            />
            <div class="hint">You must be at least 18 years old.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email <span>*</span></label>
            <input
              id="email"
              name="email"
              type="email"
              required
              autocomplete="email"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="country">Country of residence <span>*</span></label>
            <input
              id="country"
              name="country"
              type="text"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Role & request type -->
          <div class="field">
            <label for="role">What do you want to do? <span>*</span></label>
            <select id="role" name="role" required>
              <option value="">Select one</option>
              <option value="borrow">Request to borrow money</option>
              <option value="lend">Offer to lend money</option>
              <option value="both">Both borrow and lend</option>
              <option value="invest">Investment / strategy only</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="currency">Preferred currency <span>*</span></label>
            <select id="currency" name="currency" required>
              <option value="">Select currency</option>
              <option value="NOK">NOK</option>
              <option value="USD">USD</option>
              <option value="EUR">EUR</option>
              <option value="CRYPTO">Crypto (specify below)</option>
            </select>
            <div class="hint">
              If you choose crypto, add which asset in the message field.
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Work & income -->
          <div class="field">
            <label for="employment">Work situation <span>*</span></label>
            <select id="employment" name="employment_status" required>
              <option value="">Select one</option>
              <option value="full_time">Employed – full time</option>
              <option value="part_time">Employed – part time</option>
              <option value="self_employed">Self-employed</option>
              <option value="student">Student</option>
              <option value="unemployed">Unemployed</option>
              <option value="retired">Retired</option>
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="income">
              Monthly net income (approx.)
              <span>*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              id="income"
              name="monthly_income"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Example: 30 000 NOK"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Loan / lender preferences -->
          <div class="field full-width">
            <label for="loanDetails">
              If you want to borrow: loan details
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="loanDetails"
              name="loan_details"
              placeholder="Amount, purpose of the loan, desired duration, repayment plan, any collateral, etc."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="field full-width">
            <label for="lenderPreferences">
              If you want to lend: what kind of borrowers do you prefer?
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="lenderPreferences"
              name="lender_preferences"
              placeholder="Example: income level, country, risk tolerance, purpose of loan you are comfortable with, minimum/maximum amount, etc."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <!-- Investment strategy -->
          <div class="field full-width">
            <label for="investment">
              Investment & strategy requests
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="investment"
              name="investment_request"
              placeholder="Describe if you want help with an investment strategy, co-investment, or other ways to grow your money."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <!-- Extra info -->
          <div class="field full-width">
            <label for="extra">
              Anything else we should know?
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="extra"
              name="extra_information"
              placeholder="For example: experience with loans or investments, risk profile, how you heard about AmicBridge."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <!-- Compliance / confirmations -->
          <div class="field full-width">
            <div class="checkbox-row">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                id="confirmNotBank"
                name="confirm_not_bank"
                required
              />
              <label for="confirmNotBank">
                I understand that AmicBridge is a private matching network, is
                not a bank or broker, and does not hold funds for me or for any
                member.
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field full-width">
            <div class="checkbox-row">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                id="confirmRisk"
                name="confirm_risk"
                required
              />
              <label for="confirmRisk">
                I understand that all loans and investments involve risk, that I
                am responsible for my own decisions, and that nothing from
                AmicBridge is personal financial advice.
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field full-width">
            <div class="checkbox-row">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                id="confirmFee"
                name="confirm_fee"
                required
              />
              <label for="confirmFee">
                I understand that AmicBridge charges a 5&nbsp;% fee on every
                deal that is made through the network.
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit">Send request</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>How matching works</h3>
          <p class="muted">
            After you send a request, we manually review your information and
            may ask for ID documentation and additional verification. When you
            are approved, we will try to match you with other verified members
            whose preferences fit your profile and request.
          </p>
          <div class="pill-list">
            <span class="pill">ID &amp; member checks</span>
            <span class="pill">Profile-based matching</span>
            <span class="pill">Direct agreements</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Agreements and funds</h3>
          <p class="muted">
            When you agree on a loan or investment with another member, you
            sign your own agreement together (for example a loan contract) and
            transfer funds directly between yourselves using your chosen
            channels. AmicBridge does not hold or move money between members.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Risk & responsibility</h3>
          <p class="muted">
            Borrowing, lending, and investing all involve risk, including the
            possible loss of your money. Make sure you understand the terms of
            any deal, only work with people you trust, and follow the laws and
            regulations in your country. Consider getting professional advice
            before making big financial decisions.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p><strong>AmicBridge</strong> – a private network bridge for people who want to
        borrow, lend, or invest directly with each other.</p>
        <p class="warning">
          AmicBridge is not a bank, broker, or financial adviser. We do not
          guarantee returns, repayments, or the behavior of any member.
        </p>
        <p>
          Availability of our service can depend on local rules and regulations.
          By using this website and sending a request, you accept that any deal
          you make is your own responsibility.
        </p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
